{"tid":1001102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港唱片最後一店將結業　開業34年終成港人回憶","createTime":"2019-01-30T01:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T08:23:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":92,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"c6d72f8830b9ba2f238040216e45c3bae764562e","tid":1001102,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"近年不少唱片店宣告結業，去年6月香港唱片(Hong Kong Records)的太古廣場分店因連年虧蝕而結業，HMV又於上月被入稟要求還款而面臨清盤局面。種種的經營問題加上大環境驅使，唱片店的日子似乎並不好過。近日香港唱片尖沙咀分店亦宣告將於2月20日結業，成為香港唱片最後一間結業的分店，並為這屹立香港三十餘年的唱片零售品牌正式劃上句號。<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Records前身為小型唱片店「Do Re Mi」，由蕭勁展創立，原本是香港管弦樂團小提琴手的他，堅持唱片店要以音樂為主，走高雅路線。所以「Do Re Mi」於85年金鐘廊開業後，短短四年便進駐太古廣場，及後更易名為「Hong Kong Records香港唱片」，吸引不少中產樂迷成為忠實顧客。<br />\n<br />\n要問香港唱片與其他同類店鋪的不同之處，大概便是其對音樂的熱情與專業。設立爵士與古典音樂專屬房間予發燒樂迷「慢慢嘆」，香港唱片可說是同行內的先驅者。除此之外亦試過聘請DJ在場內選曲播放，提升店內的音樂氛圍，亦有效向顧客宣傳各類的音樂，提升大家的音樂品味。有網民憶述香港CD零售最輝煌的年代，香港唱片仍然比起其他品牌令人印象深刻，原因是店內職員對古典音樂也較內行，而每次入店也像是尋寶般，總能找到些大路唱片店沒在賣的唱片，永遠為樂迷帶來驚喜。只可惜此情不再，由1985年的「De Re Mi」屹立至今，香港唱片終於要向樂迷道別，成為港人的集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2381146/org/6ccbdf2bfbd155521378fff8dc5767cc.jpg/fvuzqJBI8cTUEKES6Fwe1Hfp8hD6mRHk-HvP_fh7z_0?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2381146%2Forg%2F6ccbdf2bfbd155521378fff8dc5767cc.jpg%2FfvuzqJBI8cTUEKES6Fwe1Hfp8hD6mRHk-HvP_fh7z_0%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=3a09e67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%A8%82%E5%A3%87%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81/289138/01%E7%9C%BE%E6%A8%82%E8%BF%B7-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%94%B1%E7%89%87%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%97%E5%B0%87%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E9%96%8B%E6%A5%AD34%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%82%E6%88%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A3%2587%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B3%2581%2F289138%2F01%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25BF%25B7-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2594%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD34%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2586%25B6&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=5d093862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%A8%82%E5%A3%87%E5%AF%A6%E6%B3%81/289138/01%E7%9C%BE%E6%A8%82%E8%BF%B7-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%94%B1%E7%89%87%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%97%E5%B0%87%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E9%96%8B%E6%A5%AD34%E5%B9%B4%E7%B5%82%E6%88%90%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6</a>"},{"pid":"c343ed7e9591b46f1d8eb338be51f82db89d48a1","tid":1001102,"uid":186628,"like":290,"dislike":4,"score":286,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"以為尖沙咀果間撚屌cd鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3155a482407282d062f0606a84be7ed0ccbf12","tid":1001102,"uid":61675,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"c343ed7e9591b46f1d8eb338be51f82db89d48a1","tid":1001102,"uid":186628,"like":290,"dislike":4,"score":286,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:38:36.000Z","msg":"以為尖沙咀果間撚屌cd鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:43:25.000Z","msg":"果間之前都講左真係執<br />\n大埔沙田都係"},{"pid":"6cde80428e14595ea19776f5164a3da756a8c1b3","tid":1001102,"uid":202464,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"屋企無地方，邊有位擺cd"},{"pid":"f486883729eabe54fbd1671ddaa35327a5ac497b","tid":1001102,"uid":49643,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"被時代淘汰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166d8d633c5e90c5392682c203f1bb2e39f4bc22","tid":1001102,"uid":119330,"like":9,"dislike":52,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:52:3